}Show Solution7 6Remember, references cannot be reseated, soref = ydoes not makerefa reference toy. It is equivalent tox = y.With comments explaining:#include <iostream>

int main()
{
	int x{ 4 };
	int y{ 6 };

	int& ref{ x }; // ref is now an alias for `x`
	++ref;   // x is now 5
